[{'date': {'start': {'month': None, 'day': None, 'year': 2012}, 'end': {'month': None, 'day': None, 'year': 2015}}, 'role': 'Leader in Student Work', 'company': {'id': None, 'name': "King's Church Durham", 'logo': None, 'url': None}, 'cause': None, 'description': 'I volunteered to help lead the student work at my Church. - Vision Setting. Producing a strategic vision for how students could develop throughout the year.
- Organising monthly meetings. Everything from logistics, to upfront leading, to giving talks.

- Administration. Ensured good communication between leaders and students.'}]
